[SN]TITLE[SN]
Pro12: Newport Gwent Dragons 13-0 Zebre

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Newport Gwent Dragons secured their first win of the Pro12 season but were left frustrated by Italian side Zebre.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
